(JediFlow Comprehensive Business Plan) Tj
T*
(Prepared for John) Tj
T*
(Focus: scalable lead capture, follow-up automation, and local business growth services) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. Executive Summary) Tj
T*
(JediFlow should start as a productized service that helps local businesses capture more ) Tj
T*
(leads, follow up automatically, book more appointments, and reduce manual administrative ) Tj
T*
(work. The initial wedge is outbound and lead follow-up automation. Once results are proven, ) Tj
T*
(JediFlow can expand into website upgrades, traffic generation, CRM setup, booking flows, ) Tj
T*
(review automation, and eventually software.) Tj
T*
() Tj
